import React from 'react'

import {
  Flex,
  Heading,
  Input,
  Button,
  Stack,
  FormLabel,
  FormControl,
} from '@chakra-ui/react'
// import { Container } from './styles';

function SignIn() {
  return (
    <Flex w='100vw' h='100vh' align='center' justify='center'>
      <Flex
        as='form'
        w='100%'
        maxW={360}
        bg='gray.700'
        p='8'
        borderRadius={8}
        flexDir='column'
      >
        <Stack spacing='4'>
          <FormControl>
            <FormLabel htmlFor='username'>Usuario</FormLabel>
            <Input
              id='username'
              variant='filled'
              type='text'
              name='username'
              size='lg'
            />
          </FormControl>
          <FormLabel htmlFor='password'>Senha</FormLabel>
          <Input
            id='password'
            variant='filled'
            type='password'
            name='password'
            size='lg'
          />
        </Stack>
        <Button type='submit' mt='6'>
          Entrar
        </Button>
        <Heading as='h6' size='xs' mt='6' alignSelf='center'>
          © Sisac Brasil Sistemas @2021{' '}
        </Heading>
      </Flex>
    </Flex>
  )
}

export default SignIn
